      "raw_text": "Aaron S. Watkins, candidate for\nvice-prseident on the prohibition\nnational ticket two years ago, will\narrive here this afternoon and\nspeak tonight at s o'clock at the\nCentral Christian church.\n\n\nHe is out under a speaking tour\nunder the auspices of the prohibi\nton national committee and comes\nto Spokane under the direction OF\nthe prohibition county organization\nWatkins has been conducting meet\nings in Helena and Butte."
